---
// Why Creando section highlighting the Caribbean-centered approach
---

<section class="py-12 lg:py-16 border-t border-black/10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="h2">Why Creando?</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-black/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We believe education should grow from the realities, needs, and dreams of the people who live here, not from imported models.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-[--color-spark/10] flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[--color-spark]"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="h3 mb-3">From Here, Not Elsewhere</h3>
        <p class="text-black/75">
          Built by artists and organizers who lived the gap in design education in Aruba. We connect existing efforts and build something new from within.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-[--color-sustain/10] flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[--color-sustain]"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="h3 mb-3">Hands-On & Collaborative</h3>
        <p class="text-black/75">
          Learning by doing, experimenting, and building together. We connect creative practice with local culture and the Caribbean's unique way of seeing and making.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-[--color-brand]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[--color-brand]"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="h3 mb-3">Part School, Part Laboratory</h3>
        <p class="text-black/75">
          A community space where young people develop skills, confidence, and networks to imagine and build the futures they want, right here in the Caribbean.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
